{
  "page": "Mengo Quen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> God-Emperor</span><br />Mengo Quen<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Glittering God</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nMengo Quen, third jade-green</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nGod-Emperor</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Glittering God</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jade-green_emperors\" title=\"Jade-green emperors\">Jade-green emperors</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (Mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Mengo Quen</b>, known as <b>the Glittering God</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">God-Emperor</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire_of_Yi_Ti\" title=\"Golden Empire of Yi Ti\">Golden Empire</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a> and the third member of <a href=\"/index.php/Jade-green_emperors\" title=\"Jade-green emperors\">his dynasty</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mengo_Quen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Quen earned his moniker because he ruled from a palace where the floors, walls, and columns were covered in <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> leaf, and all furnishings were made of gold, even the chamber pots.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mengo_Quen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404215823\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.262 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 523/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count